{"tid":882703,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【汪總的樓市豬手】龍市下的哈囉喂","createTime":"2018-10-30T10:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T23:17:26.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85740de3eaa5742050a0a165abf7042daa81e600","tid":882703,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"十分應景！地產市場也在這時候進入自2015年後另一次的「樓市哈囉喂」！何謂樓市哈囉喂？Halloween見到的鬼是假的，但一樣嚇人，人們都享受著其中的感受！即消費者情緒扭曲了市場的短期結果！<br />\n<br />\n樓市是應該要調節的，我在3月及6月的時候都已經發出了預警，但市場基礎結構即錢多、按揭少、息口平等都沒有改變，市場只是在上升後進入鞏固調節的階段，政府巧妙地掌握這調整階段以空置稅將累積供應在限期內出貨，和用居屋加碼折扣將草根購買力凍結，只此而已，有人推演為樓市會輾轉下跌，我不同意，市場只會調整過份樂觀的情緒泡沫及升得太快的部分而已。"},{"pid":"21fa6d42fa2e33fc293d4af95c50fb3d088b6fc1","tid":882703,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"我撰文評論樓市只是想盡代理人的本份報導我體會到的樓市實況，作為評論員，見到市場異象應該去進一步研究、弄清楚市場新常態，而不應該用文章去作意氣之爭呢！<br />\n<br />\n我當地產代理一向是我求我道！不追風，只追求自己的理想！有些人認為地產代理唱好樓市是想做生意，對不起！在財富的角度來說，我等細公司開單能帶來的利益可算是「濕濕碎」而已！講真話的最大好處是令自己滿意自己能堅持著本份的原則！很多人認為錢用了才是屬於自己的，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我做生意則認為：「因堅持原則而能放棄的生意」才是我有真本事掌握的財富，若為生意而出賣了原則，靈魂已出賣了，豈非已經是生意的奴隸了？I never！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n汪敦敬"},{"pid":"33f07915b0ff2aa9f409b8f2244e9eba72241df9","tid":882703,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181030/58853598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853598&d=em5p5Bj%2FDsQIOLZmEY4XRjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=45589da1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853598&h=9008690e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181030/58853598</a>"},{"pid":"6ea9f744a217abc375ef75c4f7db2b42a3e2f54e","tid":882703,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"龍市＞假跌＞咸豬手＞哈佬喂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340c3ed7806054570e7d8bb1764a97614392c13e","tid":882703,"uid":106247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"汪狗仲未返入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fab9cfab05dd2cdc95b857b7753f9c5829663b7","tid":882703,"uid":162526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算50%都係假跌"},{"pid":"b024fdb81383461a1ecb8f5fee8ed158d41961eb","tid":882703,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"post d 舊文出黎 J 下先<br />\n<br />\n龍市呢？"},{"pid":"6a574be0ad99587a7c274a271e466b18afbdfed2","tid":882703,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"佢班伙記出糧未，仲有佢開鋪d鋪位點解唔買要做租租？"},{"pid":"6d8865bb7b634be92d34c9c62814c2824ead588e","tid":882703,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"咁多個地產佬當中 最無恥一定係佢"},{"pid":"0cbb6a96c467aec31af3de558bb6f2d5a20cdc89","tid":882703,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8865bb7b634be92d34c9c62814c2824ead588e","tid":882703,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"咁多個地產佬當中 最無恥一定係佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T23:14:40.000Z","msg":"公公"},{"pid":"9039b81f6457906be50d9fc96eb2971fe10cc2c3","tid":882703,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"340c3ed7806054570e7d8bb1764a97614392c13e","tid":882703,"uid":106247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"汪狗仲未返入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T23:17:26.000Z","msg":"主人未走,所以青山道都咁搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}